        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 121
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "title": "Container Memory Working Set by Service (cAdvisor)",
      "description": "Actual resident memory per container (stacked), broken out by the docker-compose service name cAdvisor attaches to each cgroup. Every container now has a deploy.resources.limits.memory cap (see panel below), sized as of 2026-07-21 around 1.2-1.3x the peak observed here at the time -- not the JVM Xmx alone, since JVM processes also carry metaspace, thread stacks and direct-buffer overhead outside the heap. Use this panel going forward to watch whether any service is trending back toward its cap.",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 9,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 122
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "bytes",
