    {
      "id": 31,
      "title": "Container CPU Usage (cores) by Service",
      "description": "CPU cores actively consumed per container over the last 5m (rate of cumulative usage, not a percentage of a limit since none are set yet). Compare against the box's total core count to see headroom, and against Host CPU Utilization % above to see how much of total host CPU each service accounts for.",
